---
title: Easy Louisiana Beef & Couscous Bowl with Lemon Sour Cream & Cucumber Salad
description: Quickly-cooked beef strips meld together wonderfully with our smokey Louisiana spice blend in this Southern-inspired dish.
Make it a meal with fluffy couscous and a fresh cucumber salad, and now you’ve got a quick and easy dish that you simply can’t
miss out on!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving*
